Insurance Property & Casualty Application Overview
The Insurance Property & Casualcy Application provides examples of insurance applications for a number of lines of business that property and casualty insurers handle.
This application comprises applications, business processes, and portals, that brokers, customer service reps, claims adjusters, and administrators can use to do their jobs.
Realistic product models and rating procedures work with complete OmniScripts, Integration Procedures, and LWC-based UIs to create quotes, issue policies, endorse policies, create, and manage claims from filing through closing.

The OmniStudio data model in this org is a part of standard object model, and not OmniStudio for Vlocity.
Seed data that comes with the application includes a few pre-created quotes, policies, and claims you can examine as you get started with the application suite.

These applications can help you learn by example how to use Vlocity Insurance to design your own property and casualty insurance experiences.
